| Subnets | 15 | ~9 elevator (of 18) | 172.25.1–9.x = elevator; 172.25.10–11.x = starcity |
| Security groups | 5 | 6 elevator (of 10) | alb-external, alb-internal, be-task, fe-task, rds, **zyl-bastion-host** |
| ALB | 2 | 2 | `-alb-external` (public), `-alb-internal` |
| Target groups | 4 | 2 elevator (of 4) | `be-tg`, `fe-tg` (+ 2 starcity) |
| ECS clusters | 1 | 1 (of 2) | `zyl-elevator-prod-ecs` |
